{"tid":1536241,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港啲父母真係好撚廢","createTime":"2019-09-03T15:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:27:55.000Z","uid":2719,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8ae932f5c8df3de4103af718f4bc26b949c8ecb4","tid":1536241,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:10:16.000Z","msg":"你地啲仔女俾人追打拉告，不但唔企出黎同港共死過，反而落井下石。依家拉傷死加埋都過千個後生，應該馬上多2,3千個勇武派先係，點解仲可以咁撚沉默？如果全港父母子女一齊勇武，全城以武制暴，贏咗十世。依家要班後生獨自為戰，自己仔女日日上戰場而無動於衰。究竟啲父母受過啲咩教育，可以咁撚奴隸。如果成駕巴士嘅父母落去斬撚死班黑警，加現場同車上的後生全力反擊，遍地咁玩，有本事殺撚曬全香港人，否則你3萬狗好快死曬！"},{"pid":"c22d6ac6ed2dad5628dc046e980e2a74b2d76dae","tid":1536241,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:11:33.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.